From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: wasm fuzz harness <harness@local>
Date: Sat, 10 May 2026 00:00:00 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 3/3] avoid RawVec capacity overflow on 32-bit wasm

- VQ lookup: checked_mul for element count and for count * size_of::<f32>().
- Codebook multiplicands: reject cap * size_of::<u32>() overflow.
- Huffman desc_prog: precompute exact preorder u32 count (avoids `with_capacity(cnt)`).
- Audio residue decode: checked_mul for channel * block intermediate vectors.

---
